data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Why wait to build when this ECO FREINDLY HOME IS READY FOR YOU NOW! This delightful SOLAR PANEL home offers a truly captivating living experience. Upon arrival, you'll be captivated by the exquisite curb appeal of this beautiful property. The well-maintained landscaping and inviting entryway provide a warm and welcoming ambiance. Step inside, and you'll be greeted by a spacious and well-designed floor plan that effortlessly combines functionality and style. The heart of the home lies in the expansive living area, perfect for both casual family gatherings and formal entertaining. Natural light floods through large windows, creating an airy and inviting atmosphere. The open concept seamlessly connects the living room, dining area, and kitchen, allowing for effortless socializing and interaction. The gourmet kitchen is a chef's dream with ample cabinetry and a convenient breakfast bar. Prepare culinary delights with ease and enjoy the company of loved ones while maintaining a seamless flow throughout the main living space. Retreat to the private spaces of this residence, including the well-appointed bedrooms. The master suite is a private sanctuary, offering a serene atmosphere and ample space for relaxation. Pamper yourself in the spa-like ensuite bathroom, complete with a soaking tub, walk-in shower, and dual vanity. A generously sized his and her closets provides plenty of storage. The additional bedrooms are generously sized and offer comfort and privacy for family members or guests. Outside, a tranquil oasis awaits. Whether you desire a peaceful morning coffee or an alfresco dining experience, this outdoor space provides the perfect setting to unwind and soak in the Florida sunshine. The backyard offers a private sanctuary with no rear neighbors where you can create cherished memories and enjoy the tranquility of your own slice of paradise. There is also a garden which is a true masterpiece, meticulously landscaped to create a peaceful sanctuary. This home offers a peaceful and serene setting. Enjoy easy access to nearby parks, golf courses, shopping centers, dining options, and recreational activities. Within 10 minutes to Florida Turnpike, 45 minutes to Disney and 40 minutes to downtown. Don't miss the opportunity to own this exceptional property.
